    <div class="body">
        <p>In region Slovakia - "SK" - has changed currency in use since 1.1.2009 from 'SKK' to 'EUR'. Locale data needs update.</p>

<p>Affected method: Zend_Locale::getTranslationList('RegionToCurrency'). For returned values of this method holds:</p>

<p>ACTUAL STATUS:
 - ["EUR"] =&gt; string(92) "AD AT AX BE BL CY DE ES FI FR GF GP GR IE IT LU MC ME MF MQ MT NL PM PT QU RE SI SM TF VA YT"
 - ["SKK"] =&gt; string(2) "SK"</p>

<p>DESIRED STATUS:
 - ["EUR"] =&gt; string(92) "AD AT AX BE BL CY DE ES FI FR GF GP GR IE IT LU MC ME MF MQ MT NL PM PT QU RE SI SK SM TF VA YT"
 - ["SKK"] =&gt; [none]</p>

